title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.152 - Debris and consumer litter-operator responsibility
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.152 - Debris and consumer litter-operator responsibility

State Regulations

The operator of a mobile food service establishment or pushcart is responsible for cleanup of debris caused by the operation and consumer littering. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10

14-4.152

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
